structure.unit: COUNTIES, CITIES, AND OTHER LOCAL UNITS
ISSUANCE OF BONDS AND CONTROL OF FUNDS

law.history: Repealed 1980 Ky. Acts ch. 234, sec. 11, effective July 15, 1980. -- Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. secs. 186b-5, 186b-7, 186b-8.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Bonds of city of first class, election to permit sale at higher interest rate or below par.
